description:
On Christmas Eve, Salem’s (Nick Bakay) crazy antics push Sabrina (Melissa Joan Hart) over the edge, especially after he shreds her favorite sweater. But when she leaves him behind in frustration, and a neighborhood kid kidnaps him, Sabrina’s quiet night turns into a frantic door-to-door search to bring him home. Season 1, Episode 11: A Girl & Her Cat.
